title: Women’s Cross Country Takes Third at 2015 PSAC Championships; Norton Earns First Team Honors (Shippensburg ...
text: ( Source : Shippensburg University Athletics ) Junior Casey Norton finished ninth overall on Saturday to pace the Shippensburg University women's cross country team in placing third at the 2015 Pennsylvania State Athletic Conference ( PSAC )
